20:18.640 --> 20:20.596
I doubt it.

20:22.640 --> 20:23.959
Adam.

20:24.040 --> 20:27.157
Here, I wanted salt and vinegar.
- It doesn't matter.

20:27.240 --> 20:30.073
We don't like prawn cocktail.
- Really. It doesn't matter.

20:30.160 --> 20:32.151
I'll change them.
- No, stop!

20:32.760 --> 20:34.193
Sit down!

20:35.200 --> 20:37.156
All right, all right.

20:38.320 --> 20:41.949
I have something to tell you.
You mustn't tell a soul.

20:42.040 --> 20:44.110
Sure.
- I'm serious.

20:44.200 --> 20:45.679
What, no-one?
- No-one.

20:45.760 --> 20:47.273
Not even Giggsy?

20:48.120 --> 20:49.553
Not even Giggsy.

20:49.640 --> 20:51.596
OK. I give you my word.

20:53.040 --> 20:55.156
Forget it. It doesn't matter.

20:55.240 --> 20:56.559
What?
- Change the crisps.

20:56.640 --> 20:58.551
Bollocks to that! What is it?

20:58.640 --> 21:01.837
You can't ask me to keep a secret,
then clam up.

21:01.920 --> 21:04.878
It'd be wrong to involve you.
- Let me make that decision.

21:04.960 --> 21:07.428
I want to be involved. We're mates.

21:09.760 --> 21:11.671
I'm cheating on Jenny.

21:11.760 --> 21:13.637
Yeah, right!
- No, really.

21:13.720 --> 21:16.154
And the fruit machine here pays a jackpot!

21:16.240 --> 21:18.151
Believe it. It's true.

21:19.720 --> 21:21.438
Yes!

21:21.520 --> 21:23.476
Hold on. Wait a minute.

21:24.720 --> 21:26.631
Who with?

21:26.720 --> 21:28.438
Amy from work.

21:28.520 --> 21:29.873
Amy who's nuts?

21:29.960 --> 21:33.270
She's not.
She's sympathetic and understanding.

21:33.360 --> 21:35.271
Yeah, and nuts.

21:35.360 --> 21:37.271
Are you out of your mind?

21:37.360 --> 21:38.679
I know she is.

21:39.720 --> 21:41.676
How did this happen?

21:41.760 --> 21:45.196
You know how me and Jenny
haven't been getting along?

21:45.280 --> 21:47.191
Yep.

21:47.280 --> 21:49.191
<i>Of course you do.</i>

21:49.280 --> 21:51.794
We were on this Outward Bound thing,

21:51.880 --> 21:55.509
and it started raining
and we got soaked to the skin.

21:55.600 --> 21:58.876
From there it's a short step to sex!
- No, we got lost in the woods.

21:58.960 --> 22:01.394
You did it in the woods?
- No. In a motel.

22:01.480 --> 22:03.232
God, how...sordid.

22:03.320 --> 22:05.675
It was a nice motel. I couldn't stop myself.

22:05.760 --> 22:07.671
Cos she's a nymphomaniac.

22:07.760 --> 22:09.432
No, she's not.
- She was with me.

22:09.520 --> 22:10.873
She wanted to keep you.

22:10.960 --> 22:14.077
You don't understand her.
She's quite sensitive.

22:14.160 --> 22:17.232
You didn't deserve her.
- Jenny doesn't deserve you!

22:17.320 --> 22:21.199
Does she know about this?
- Of course not! She mustn't find out.

22:23.240 --> 22:25.879
You promised!
- Before I knew what it was.

22:25.960 --> 22:28.315
She'd kill me!
- No more than you deserve.

22:30.720 --> 22:31.789
Hang on.

22:31.880 --> 22:36.510
She says she doesn't love me any more
and tries to get off with you!

22:41.160 --> 22:43.071
Jen made a fool of herself, right?

22:43.160 --> 22:44.832
She regrets it.

22:44.920 --> 22:49.869
She's trying to repair the damage,
but what you're dolng, Pete...

22:49.960 --> 22:51.871
God...

22:51.960 --> 22:54.793
Where are you going?
- Home.

22:54.880 --> 22:56.791
Oh, cheers. Thanks.

22:56.880 --> 22:59.678
Thanks for being supportive!
- I'm not doing supportive.

22:59.760 --> 23:01.716
Try Amy.

23:12.360 --> 23:14.351
You're in agony, aren't you?

23:14.440 --> 23:16.351
No, just a bit of pain.

23:16.440 --> 23:18.396
No more than childbirth.

23:20.280 --> 23:22.874
I've finished. Not a bad job, is it?

23:22.960 --> 23:24.712
It's almost like a gecko.

23:24.800 --> 23:25.869
That wasn't too bad.

23:25.960 --> 23:27.632
You were passed out!

23:27.720 --> 23:29.153
What does it look like?

23:29.240 --> 23:30.912
It's really not that bad.

23:32.200 --> 23:34.430
Are you getting one done?
- No.

23:36.040 --> 23:37.473
No!

23:44.240 --> 23:47.516
Ramona! So sorry! I thought you were Karen.

23:48.640 --> 23:50.596
I'm terribly sorry.

23:53.600 --> 23:55.556
Karen.

23:56.600 --> 23:58.716
I've just assaulted Ramona.

23:58.800 --> 23:59.789
What? Why?

23:59.880 --> 24:01.552
I thought she was you.

24:02.600 --> 24:04.909
She was bending over and...you know,

24:05.000 --> 24:06.911
gander, gander, goosey.

24:07.000 --> 24:08.479
David, you know I hate that.

24:08.560 --> 24:11.757
I didn't know it was her.
She had your dress on.

24:11.840 --> 24:14.479
The Prada.
- Prada?

24:14.560 --> 24:16.755
Or Jil Sander, if it was a yellow one.

24:16.840 --> 24:19.638
It was black.
- Yeah, that is Prada.

24:19.720 --> 24:21.631
You gave her two dresses?

24:21.720 --> 24:23.995
Three, actually. The rest,
I gave to charity.

24:24.080 --> 24:25.593
What?

24:25.680 --> 24:29.309
I don't want them, so I gave them
to a good cause. Pass me a towel.

24:29.400 --> 24:31.223
Why not help the starving in Africa?

24:31.718 --> 24:34.394
They're as thin as supermodels,
they can dress like them.

24:34.480 --> 24:36.516
Right, I'm going to sort out Ramona.

24:36.600 --> 24:40.354
You have a smudge on your back.
- It's a tattoo, and it's a gecko.

24:40.440 --> 24:42.749
A tattoo? Are you out of your mind?

24:42.840 --> 24:44.831
Don't you like geckos?

24:44.920 --> 24:46.319
Why did you get a tattoo?

24:46.400 --> 24:48.516
David, I just thought it would be fun.

24:50.000 --> 24:52.275
Fun?
- David, you're doing it again.

24:52.360 --> 24:53.793
Stop repeating what I say.

24:53.880 --> 24:56.633
Fun? Tattoos are permanent, you know.

24:56.720 --> 24:58.790
What are we going to tell Josh?

24:58.880 --> 25:01.633
- ''Mummy was a Hell's Angel''?
- David, it's body art.

25:01.720 --> 25:06.077
I'm seriously worried about you.
Smoking dope at dinner parties,

25:06.160 --> 25:10.756
giving designer dresses to Oxfam,
and now mutilating yourself.

25:10.840 --> 25:14.913
And you're a model citizen -
apart from sexually harassing the nanny!

25:16.400 --> 25:19.312
Was that Adam?
- No, wrong number, love.

25:19.400 --> 25:23.109
Is he coming out for a drink?
Are we meeting him there?

25:23.200 --> 25:26.909
We're running late,
so we're probably best meeting him there.

25:27.000 --> 25:28.956
All right.

25:39.640 --> 25:41.596
Amanda Wagstaff!

25:43.320 --> 25:44.912
No.

25:45.960 --> 25:47.552
Hi. Remember me?

25:48.400 --> 25:50.038
No.

25:51.080 --> 25:53.036
Fancy a shag?

25:53.840 --> 25:55.751
Yeah!

25:57.840 --> 26:00.991
Please leave a message for David,
Karen and Josh...

26:01.080 --> 26:03.196
or Ramona, after the tone.

26:04.400 --> 26:08.791
Karen, it's Rachel.
You owe me one and I'm calling it in.

26:08.880 --> 26:12.873
I said I'd go to Adam's school reunion
and I can't make it.

26:12.960 --> 26:14.871
